// Property-check runner for the BIP-340 Schnorr spec. SHA-256 is an abstract
// (uninterpreted) primitive, so the sign/verify correctness properties are SAW
// :prove targets, not randomized-:check targets. Here we check the structural
// (SHA-free) properties: even-Y key normalization and its idempotence.
:load Secp256k1Schnorr.cry
:set tests=5
:check normalised_key_has_even_y
:check normalise_key_idempotent
